channel.title: Takeshi's castle
channel.description:
There is this commercial on the Dutch Comedy central for Takeshi's castle. In the background they play a Japanese song, which for some odd reason sounds quite good. But I have no idea who sings it, or the title of the song. So are there any Dutch members that happen to know the name of the song/woman who sings it? Or even has a link to the commercial or to the song itself?
TENK YOU!
